{"tid":1466784,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果今次再重犯2014 嘅錯，香港人呢世都唔配有民主","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:37.000Z","uid":37396,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"541382eb5efd417e0d9118c7232b3b5eaafff041","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:16.000Z","msg":"無錯，今晚可能係有人做得唔好<br />\n但唔該記住我地係一team 人<br />\n有錯就去糾正，然後繼續下一步<br />\n唔係互屌<br />\n<br />\n今次係我地最後機會<br />\n輸咗就真係無架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記今次運動嘅宗旨<br />\n<br />\n1. 和理非同勇武，缺一不可<br />\n2. 兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n3. 不分化 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n4. 核彈都唔割<br />\n5. 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未輸</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f2b2b5c63b653b12a011dc2d30d860994b6b8ab","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418a4e34b0b4021c62b6e83506ee7ee39eec1ee4","tid":1466784,"uid":51266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1b5ffa97cdf27e1f6a114ac7b0eb0fb0c43e5f4","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7eca4ccad0ea73826b2fa24bf1358495cc1c10b","tid":1466784,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n事情已經發生左<br />\n而家重點係要諗點補返個鑊<br />\n民間記者會又好<br />\n文宣又好<br />\n道歉又好<br />\n總之而家最優先係要補救錯誤<br />\n就算係覺得今日行動唔好<br />\n核彈都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"900f15da8c0c84d48eb877f4df1ece5fdd360fcb","tid":1466784,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"其實咩行動都試過<br />\n所以真係應該抱住做得唔好就做好佢既心態 繼續做<br />\n<br />\n否則 其實都冇咩活動示威者係未做過"},{"pid":"182749cc9cf29dc5fe055e3aed5cbb43f378bf44","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5abca95d5321222375ef41ae84b61349f616270b","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ffcf1a1da7c5629812ca50234f63ae1c1749fe","tid":1466784,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"機場一役喺要喺「公安」同「醫護第一」之間取決一方，從而比對家分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1465094/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對中共黎講犧牲一個公安<br />\n同收買一個金毛MK仔同收買啲人扮勇武掉野去警車唔係無可能<br />\n搵幾個人就挑起到你地內鬥<br />\n圍左公安咁耐有無得著？對五大訴求有無幫助？<br />\n唔喺幫個公安講說話，而喺處事要為大局著想<br />\n圍左三、四個鐘頭先上到醫護車<br />\n之後個金毛MK仔即刻第一時間沖出馬路靜坐阻路<br />\n我就覺得成年事好鬼鬼<br />\n根本喺一場中共/黑警Show<br />\n最大敵人根本就係你地自己<br />\n要時刻都有批判性思考<br />\n入得機場和理非就和理非<br />\n比中共睇穿你班人「好憎公安」同「讓路比醫護」兩者之間做出決定<br />\n萬死個公安死左就有位比人入<br />\n但就係咁比人分化你話抵唔抵？"},{"pid":"b131cb08d342ddf231e478716158bd5dde845143","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8f2f5c07f60e972042b4680caed393122ae68","tid":1466784,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}